{"tid":1190580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"69唔係嘉年華 69唔係嘉年華","createTime":"2019-06-07T11:30:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T17:05:49.000Z","uid":24284,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e2012d9e9671143918540276bcdf36ec7a7fed73","tid":1190580,"uid":24284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T11:30:08.000Z","msg":"雖然民陣係垃圾，一定行完即刻嗌散水<br />\n我亦唔知會唔會有下場，但呢個係心態問題<br />\n<br />\n遊行人士應該做好任何行動升級既心理準備<br />\n黑衫褲、口罩、尿袋、閂Face ID/Touch ID 等等<br />\n保護好你既同伴、女士、老幼<br />\n如果你一人行(尤其係女士)，應該跟貼人群，並且定時向親人報平安<br />\n<br />\n69對我黎講除左係反送中惡法遊行，更加係愛港遊行<br />\n到時見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56be3e315fabc46bb63a52afebcd88934fe2e7c7","tid":1190580,"uid":24284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T11:34:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"861ff1082998bba08483c23e5bc867258c62c705","tid":1190580,"uid":24284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T11:49:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32f5ba4d91cadfb58a97dad01d3a3f78d00d7693","tid":1190580,"uid":24284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T12:34:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb4aacdcab02ff4597bb720b0adc0d6dc51f9779","tid":1190580,"uid":226955,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T12:34:49.000Z","msg":"何謂遊行：<br />\n遊行嘅意義絕對唔係指齋行完就算，而係話比當權者，我宜家街上有（假設）五十萬人，如果你唔聽我地講野，我唔擔保呢幾十萬人會做啲咩野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n愛因斯坦 (Albert Einstein)：「The world will not be destoryed by those who do evil, but by these who watch them without doing anything.(這個世界不會被那些作惡多端的人毀滅，而是冷眼旁觀、選擇保持緘默的人)」；鄭有傑(導演):「良心的沉默是邪惡的幫兇。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好多時歷史中嘅轉折位都係由表面上微不足道嘅小事/小人物而形成嘅，所以我地更加唔可以睇小自己<br />\n<br />\n6月9號一齊去遊行！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f914a8d76917f1b1562fb3f100db7f67ef43b4f5","tid":1190580,"uid":24284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T14:15:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3de26c5c12bd66dfb4dafa18419be5f2eed78ddc","tid":1190580,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T14:18:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a55885b114c07eece80aa7185b3c65f6f3fe1342","tid":1190580,"uid":24284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T02:35:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cca0667847c9d5afc3ef5fbfcad269af23f9cc22","tid":1190580,"uid":89834,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T02:36:42.000Z","msg":"又想叫人衝？你自己唔帶頭？"},{"pid":"07da3f1be2abf52ff8168545ff944c166d852231","tid":1190580,"uid":52230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T02:37:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>槍口一致對外！<br />\n<br />\n不要分化，不要懷疑隊友！<br />\n<br />\n有人被捕立即集體救援！<br />\n<br />\n保護同伴！<br />\n<br />\n6.9 GOGOGO!</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c7fac152ada5aa8e5fd16827a9de8e34d8be118","tid":1190580,"uid":24284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07da3f1be2abf52ff8168545ff944c166d852231","tid":1190580,"uid":52230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T02:37:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>槍口一致對外！<br />\n<br />\n不要分化，不要懷疑隊友